## id: postman-collection-exposure
## name: Postman Collection Exposure
## author: hack007x
## severity: low
## tags: api,postman,exposure,discovery
## description: Detected exposed Postman collection JSON files that contained API endpoints and environment details. These files were publicly accessible and disclosed authentication headers and other sensitive information.
## reference: https://medium.com/@utkarshporwal24/exposed-postman-collections-ed6086b96ba5
## shodan-query: http.html:"postman.json"
## verification: true

GET /postman.json HTTP/1.1
Host: {{Hostname}}
User-Agent: {{random_ua}}

#@ stop_scan: true
#@ condition: and
#@ matcher: header["content-type"] matches /(?i)content-type:\s*application\/(json|vnd\.postman\.[^;\s]+)/
#@ matcher: body matches /(?i)"info"\s*:\s*\{\s*"name"\s*:\s*".+?"/
#@ matcher: body matches /(?i)"item"\s*:\s*\[/
#@ matcher: status_code == 200

---

GET /docs/postman.json HTTP/1.1
Host: {{Hostname}}
User-Agent: {{random_ua}}

#@ stop_scan: true
#@ condition: and
#@ matcher: header["content-type"] matches /(?i)content-type:\s*application\/(json|vnd\.postman\.[^;\s]+)/
#@ matcher: body matches /(?i)"info"\s*:\s*\{\s*"name"\s*:\s*".+?"/
#@ matcher: body matches /(?i)"item"\s*:\s*\[/
#@ matcher: status_code == 200

---

